data.description: Fresh exterior paint surrounds this attractive 1-story on creek lot where lush hearty, native landscaping with beautiful color sweeps along entry drive & along front! Impressive moldings & millwork embellish the open living & dining with added recessed lighting. Fireplace offers charm to living room with  access to covered deck. Kitchen & master bath have been updated with desirable finishes. Kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & updated pulls. Master bath is fashioned with wood like Vanity and guest bath was just refurbished. Partially covered deck wraps envelops backyard retreat with step-down area to relax overlooking backyard play area along creek. Find fresh paint in many rooms plus a full-size utility room & spacious garage with exterior entrance, workbench & abundant storage shelves. All bedrooms feature walk in closet space!
